snippet.title: Bananas!!! A free game for iOS & Android
snippet.description:
Bananas!!! ia a FREE game for iOS & Android.

Download for Android: http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.studioavante.BananasDroid
Download for iPhone / iPad: http://appstore.com/studioavante/bananas
Developed by Studio Avante: http://www.studioavante.com
Music by Pulselooper: http://www.chippanze.org
The Bananometer: http://www.playbananas.com
